data.description: 55+ Real 3BR/2 Bath, in a move in condition. Large 290 sf' enclosed patio with an exit to a beautiful, open and  private backyard along a long canal.  Split BR's &, Cathedral ceiling with 2 skylights. Many cabinets in Kitchen. Laundry , appliances. A/C & hot water. Garage + 2. Community has many activities yet quiet. Amenities includes: Gated, heated pool. Jacuzzi, saunas (dry/steam), gym, tennis, Pickleball, bocce, basketball, walking path around 3 beautiful lakes, theater & more . Location is perfect. Near the club house & the sport center with a quick access to all major roads & short distance to the beach. Shopping, restaurants & downtown actions. Board approval up to 30 day. Owner is very reasonable, eager & ready for a serious buyer
